{"tid":379614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯寫英文信: the superpower they versus was the rule of law","createTime":"2017-08-29T13:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T10:35:43.000Z","uid":76115,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"475d4beb72f070b612b670cf4107d9d14aaa25db","tid":379614,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:07:46.000Z","msg":"喺馮睎乾專欄引用見到, 唔得閒上佢fb搵原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/9dP3kv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F9dP3kv&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1542b295\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/9dP3kv</a><br />\n<br />\n何博士為自拍可以去到幾盡，不得而知；但我肯定，全人類也無法阻止他寫信。去年他用英文寫信給律政司，我曾撰文點評，今天瀏覽他的臉書，依然見他筆耕不輟，不是去信李國章，就是致函《紐約時報》（反駁兩篇評論三子判囚的文章）。但他寫給《紐》的信，刊登機會應該很渺茫，主因是文筆，例如有句寫「<strong>and the superpower that they versus was the rule of law</strong>」，「they」指黃之鋒等三人，大意我明白，但堂堂律師博士，居然把「versus」這前置詞或連接詞誤當動詞用？以一位香港執業律師來說，這英文水平實在震驚七十億人。至於說戴耀廷荼毒青年<br />\n<br />\n有無咁撚誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4140d89daba4b55b8ae65cd91dc86dd26a6d3686","tid":379614,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺馮睎乾專欄引用見到, 唔得閒上佢fb搵原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/9dP3kv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F9dP3kv&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1542b295\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/9dP3kv</a><br />\n<br />\n何博士為自拍可以去到幾盡，不得而知；但我肯定，全人類也無法阻止他寫信。去年他用英文寫信給律政司，我曾撰文點評，今天瀏覽他的臉書，依然見他筆耕不輟，不是去信李國章，就是致函《紐約時報》（反駁兩篇評論三子判囚的文章）。但他寫給《紐》的信，刊登機會應該很渺茫，主因是文筆，例如有句寫「<strong>and the superpower that they versus was the rule of law</strong>」，「they」指黃之鋒等三人，大意我明白，但堂堂律師博士，居然把「versus」這前置詞或連接詞誤當動詞用？以一位香港執業律師來說，這英文水平實在震驚七十億人。至於說戴耀廷荼毒青年<br />\n<br />\n有無咁撚誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nstand against? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3870506baeba71213827ecc98417ec52423dcce4","tid":379614,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:10:02.000Z","msg":"好出奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9850bc43432b18bf265c321edcedb7f934244c30","tid":379614,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:11:11.000Z","msg":"佢同佢老死泰博屎都幾襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/16826062_718372338337126_1256468034664815028_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F16826062_718372338337126_1256468034664815028_o.jpg&h=b5f5d7a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/16903517_718372335003793_7380933932198908393_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F16903517_718372335003793_7380933932198908393_o.jpg&h=f7ad5ab5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"858f456c06cdcf24a0912f7dc123e9284d6e2029","tid":379614,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"佢唔係律師黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"bba1eabd379fccbd345439040a0e1c8977833c30","tid":379614,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢唔係律師黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n同問"},{"pid":"c1bb4e0e4654258b7b812d389cdfb23ff7f0d115","tid":379614,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢唔係律師黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n同問</blockquote><br />\n1975-1979 在皇仁書院接受中學教育<br />\n1979-1984 在英國攻讀高中之後加入英國州瑪高等教育學院（現改名為安格里亞魯斯金大學）取得榮譽法律學士學位<br />\n1984-1986 回港後修讀香港大學專業法律文憑課程<br />\n2011 獲安格里亞魯斯金大學頒授榮譽法學博士學位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請槍砟化"},{"pid":"d19d4a1f5a978044af005b5104cf3dc7cb643b52","tid":379614,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢唔係律師黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n同問</blockquote><br />\n1975-1979 在皇仁書院接受中學教育<br />\n1979-1984 在英國攻讀高中之後加入英國州瑪高等教育學院（現改名為安格里亞魯斯金大學）取得榮譽法律學士學位<br />\n1984-1986 回港後修讀香港大學專業法律文憑課程<br />\n2011 獲安格里亞魯斯金大學頒授榮譽法學博士學位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請槍砟化</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anglia_Ruskin_University\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAnglia_Ruskin_University&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0d814c41\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anglia_Ruskin_University</a><br />\nIt has been listed in the Times Higher Education&rsquo;s (THE) World University Rankings &ndash; being named as one of the top 350 institutions in the world and joint 38th best in the UK.<br />\n<br />\n唔係名校但都遠非野雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09bc51d321ac00785736b2bbafb19b9eca413c3","tid":379614,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:24:23.000Z","msg":"咁樣考AL 既話UE 都過唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c152a84b33fba035ca117eceeb9f06fc93bd444","tid":379614,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樣考AL 既話UE 都過唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇改卷員；唔一定知 versus  係 preposition；當咗係 &quot;facing&quot; 咁，好似南華對東方"},{"pid":"0c2232a8e90e95a0655430b5dd019d6799de6c17","tid":379614,"uid":72906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:05:15.000Z","msg":"是但啦, 理得佢文筆好唔好, Don't make stupid person famous ok?"},{"pid":"5a54090c7cda8d355f3761b8bca9d086c9b6e390","tid":379614,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:05:28.000Z","msg":"challenge ?"},{"pid":"97078583bb03511c5d72515fffcb4c9f0c1a1610","tid":379614,"uid":131691,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢唔係律師黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n同問</blockquote><br />\n1975-1979 在皇仁書院接受中學教育<br />\n1979-1984 在英國攻讀高中之後加入英國州瑪高等教育學院（現改名為安格里亞魯斯金大學）取得榮譽法律學士學位<br />\n1984-1986 回港後修讀香港大學專業法律文憑課程<br />\n2011 獲安格里亞魯斯金大學頒授榮譽法學博士學位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請槍砟化</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anglia_Ruskin_University\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAnglia_Ruskin_University&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0d814c41\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anglia_Ruskin_University</a><br />\nIt has been listed in the Times Higher Education&rsquo;s (THE) World University Rankings &ndash; being named as one of the top 350 institutions in the world and joint 38th best in the UK.<br />\n<br />\n唔係名校但都遠非野雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Anglia Ruskin 係出名嘢嚟㗎！</span><br />\n<br />\nAnglia Ruskin 出名在於佢座落於劍橋城，但又唔係劍橋大學嘅大學。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tcs.cam.ac.uk/assets/news/thumbs/main/Photo-Ben-Verth.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tcs.cam.ac.uk%2Fassets%2Fnews%2Fthumbs%2Fmain%2FPhoto-Ben-Verth.jpg&h=6d79404f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n👆劍橋火車站，一落車就係佢嘅廣告<br />\n<br />\nAnglia Ruskin 同 Oxford Brookes 一樣，係一班敗類就去讀完之後話畀人聽「係呀，我大學去咗劍橋、牛津讀㗎」嘅大學<br />\n<br />\n係比野雞大學更核突嘅大學<br />\n<br />\n利申：劍記人"},{"pid":"41b69d48268b7cbf463d5fb54b6297b7c2e86ac1","tid":379614,"uid":609,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:16:44.000Z","msg":"其實佢中過風 會嚴重影響大腦語言區域 <br />\n仲作到完整句子真係算係咁"},{"pid":"1d1af3f7d105fa9d18f2c7a124943938620d4037","tid":379614,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"佢間大學咁都唔叫野雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申： 讀英國野雞大學"},{"pid":"06f3edbd200c55a59da33280f510ebd1b021dfc5","tid":379614,"uid":40839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:36:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢唔係律師黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n同問</blockquote><br />\n1975-1979 在皇仁書院接受中學教育<br />\n1979-1984 在英國攻讀高中之後加入英國州瑪高等教育學院（現改名為安格里亞魯斯金大學）取得榮譽法律學士學位<br />\n1984-1986 回港後修讀香港大學專業法律文憑課程<br />\n2011 獲安格里亞魯斯金大學頒授榮譽法學博士學位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請槍砟化</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anglia_Ruskin_University\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAnglia_Ruskin_University&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0d814c41\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anglia_Ruskin_University</a><br />\nIt has been listed in the Times Higher Education&rsquo;s (THE) World University Rankings &ndash; being named as one of the top 350 institutions in the world and joint 38th best in the UK.<br />\n<br />\n唔係名校但都遠非野雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAnglia Ruskin垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 唔係睇排名 一早識呢間垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc753d7b83732a8211462130ceb97e598d79b1d2","tid":379614,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"生於香港。父親戴均為元朗鄉紳。<br />\n<br />\n1985年當選為元朗區議員。同年9月從選舉團晉身立法局。1988年連任立法局議員。1991年在立法局新界西直選中當選，不久後卻以「私人理由」放棄議席。其後被揭發以假文件獲得律師資格，被法庭裁定5項偽造文件冒充律師資格及向律師公會發假誓等罪成。1993年3月被判即時入獄9個月。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%88%B4%E5%B1%95%E8%8F%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%25B1%2595%25E8%258F%25AF&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4b80e4dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%88%B4%E5%B1%95%E8%8F%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哪，我講既係戴展華，唔係何君妖呀。"},{"pid":"bfc62b6d949fbf3f0ccc3d7eb9b4c1cdbc6ab676","tid":379614,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢唔係律師黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n同問</blockquote><br />\n1975-1979 在皇仁書院接受中學教育<br />\n1979-1984 在英國攻讀高中之後加入英國州瑪高等教育學院（現改名為安格里亞魯斯金大學）取得榮譽法律學士學位<br />\n1984-1986 回港後修讀香港大學專業法律文憑課程<br />\n2011 獲安格里亞魯斯金大學頒授榮譽法學博士學位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請槍砟化</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anglia_Ruskin_University\" data-sr-url=\"https